				text-center font-semibold 
				border-t-2 border-surface-200/40
				pt-6 opacity-70 
				text-surface-200 dark:text-surface-100">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Mist Media. {footerTranslations.rights_reserved[locale.get()]}
		</span>
   </div>
</footer>
